assed through each other as is observed decreases\nthis number to only 0.1. The discovery of more such systems would thus indeed\npresent a challenge to the standard cosmology.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 24 Dec 2014 17:37:40 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 6 Apr 2015 17:10:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-04-30"}
