ollide with magnetic white dwarfs $B\\sim\n10^9$G. The distinctive feature is that the durations of the bursts are of the\norder of $0.1$second.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 25 Dec 2014 13:42:56 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 12 Jan 2015 13:34:39 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 7 Mar 2015 03:08:10 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Mon, 20 Apr 2015 07:34:59 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Tue, 17 Nov 2015 00:16:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-11-18"}
